OL,5, The family of a "loving" mother killed 
OL,6, in a car crash with her teenage son    
OL,7, said Christmas would be "immensely     
OL,8, difficult" without them.               
OL,10,FFormer theatre worker Clair, 42, and   
OL,11,F15-year-old Year 11 pupil Sam, died at 
OL,12,Fthe scene of the crash Ripponden Road, 
OL,13,FOldham. Their surnames were not given. 
OL,15,FA 13-year-old passenger was also       
OL,16,Fseriously hurt in the crash, on        
OL,17,FSaturday, police said.                 
OL,19,FThe 35-year-old driver of the other car
OL,20,Fwas arrested and remained in custody.  
